title: SHOOT First: Bett and Byron (from DHP 34-36) (2014|Dgtl|Empire)
description:
This is "SHOOT First: Bett and Byron", serialized in "Dark Horse Presents" issues 34 thru 36.

The story is an adjunct to the four-issue series which concluded early this year
(  <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9484718" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9484718</a>   ), focussing on the two titular characters and their relationship, before, during, and after the events covered in said issues.

By Justin Aclin, whose principal claim to fame appear to be his contributions to "Twisted ToyFare Theatre" ( <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Twisted_ToyFare_Theatre" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Twisted_ToyFare_Theatre</a>  ).
